folder: Stuart Street & Avenue U, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Stuart St., east side, between Aves., U and V. The view shows the Whitney Mansion and Barns. This neighborhood has changed considerably; house still standing in 1936.

February 26, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(2)
The same, from another angle.

February 26, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.

(3)
The same, one of the buildings on the estate.

February 26, 1931.

P. L. Sperr.
